==English==
===Etymology===
from ''hyper-'' above, extra  +  ''-(o)nym'' name.  in Gk.: υπερνύμιον, literally meaning 'extra name'.

===Noun===
'''hypernym'''

#{{linguistics}} a [[superordinate]] grouping word which includes [[subordinate]] grouping word(s).
#:''"musical instrument" is a '''hypernym''' of "guitar", because "musical instrument" includes "guitar".''

